name: Caining_Huang_Finalproject
description: There are three levels in total, and you can move from one to  another. First you enter a gallery, and you will find there are two pictures on the wall, touch the picture, and you can get into the picture.  One picture depicts a village, the place you are standing is beside a river. you can get on the boat, and there is a hole on the mountain on the other side of the river.  You need to  squat down to move through it. There are also many bamboos, you can cut them down using an axe. The other picture is a café, you can break the chairs and bottles in the room.
